            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前華為發布了全新旗艦三摺疊手機 Mate XT 非凡大師，2 日前我們報道過預購額已達 200 萬部，甚至有二手平台表示願意基於原價額外加 1.6 萬元收機（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/09/huawei-mate-xt-2mill-order/fun-tech/">相關報道</a>）。今日小編瀏覽華為商城發現，現時 Mate XT 已經有近 550 萬預訂訂單，中國著名二手平台「閒魚」上亦有不少華為 Mate XT 放盤，最高驚見 19.9 萬元人民幣（約港幣 21.90 萬元）</p><p>距離預約結束仍有 7 日，華為商城今日下午 6 點半數據顯示，目前已有 549.7 萬人預訂 Mate XT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/huaweimatext1-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/huaweimatext1-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/huaweimatext1.jpg 1212w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲目前已經有 549.7 萬人次預訂華為 Mate XT， 圖片來源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/comdetail/index.html?prdId=10086499369393">VMALL</a></p><p>中國最大的二手物品交易平台「閒魚」可見，華為 Mate XT 售價由原價至 5 萬元不等，其中最高售價驚見 19.99 萬元人民幣（約港幣 21.9 萬元），仍然有 3 個人表示有興趣購買。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912183735-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912183735-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912183735.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.goofish.com/search?spm=a21ybx.home.searchSuggest.1.4c053da63QwuXh&amp;q=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BAmate%E9%9D%9E%E5%87%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88xt">Goofish</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912184239-368x580.jpg" alt="" width="368" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912184239-368x580.jpg 368w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912184239.jpg 571w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 368px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高驚見人民幣 19.99 萬元，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.goofish.com/search?spm=a21ybx.home.searchSuggest.1.4c053da63QwuXh&amp;q=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BAmate%E9%9D%9E%E5%87%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88xt">Goofish</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.vmall.com/product/comdetail/index.html?prdId=10086499369393">華為商城</a>、<a href="https://www.goofish.com/search?spm=a21ybx.home.searchSuggest.1.4c053da63QwuXh&amp;q=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BAmate%E9%9D%9E%E5%87%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88xt">閒魚</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/huaweimatextud-firstlook/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Huawei Mate XT Ultimate Design 非凡大師現場評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/13/huawei-mate-xt-ultimate-design-kirin-9010/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為 Mate XT 處理器確認，效能被指屬中階水平</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/how-to-talk-on-huawei-mate-xt/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">華為 Mate XT 三摺機應如何聽電話　網民：招搖過市易招賊</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/huawei-mate-xt-200k-rmb/mobile-phone/">華為 Mate XT 三摺機炒價見 22 萬港元　預訂開放 3 日接 550 萬部訂單</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
